<figureCitation box="[159,287,1733,1758]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 15" captionStartId="3.[151,263,1738,1759]" captionTargetBox="[190,1394,195,1718]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[190,1395,195,1719]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 15. Atrovirensis spp., adults. 1. A. atrovirens, Nepal (after Gyulai et al. 2013); 2. A. annamita, HT, Vietnam (after Gyulai et al. 2013); 3. A. parannamita sp. n., male HT, China, Aut. Reg. Xizang, genit. prep. HHL- 2930 - 1; 4. A. parannamita sp. n., female PT, China, Aut. Reg. Xizang, genit. prep. HHL- 2906 - 2; 5. A. pedibus, HT, China, Prov. Hubei (after Gyulai et al. 2013); 6. A. sp. cf. A. parannamita, male, China, Aut. Reg. Xizang, genit. prep. HHL- 2907 - 1; 7. A. sinica, HT, China, Prov. Guangdong, genit. prep. ZFMK 1624; 8. A. owadai, Prov. Guangdong, HT, China (after Gyulai et al. 2013); 9. A. taiwani, HT, Taiwan (after Gyulai et al. 2013); 10. A. furcatus sp. n., male HT, China, Prov. Guangdong, genit. prep. HHL- 2921 - 1; 11. A. furcatus sp. n., female PT, China, Prov. Guangdong, genit. prep. HHL- 2919 - 2; 12. A. sp. cf. furcatus, male, China, Prov. Guangdong, genit. prep. HHL- 2918 - 1; 13. A. sp. cf. furcatus, female, China, Prov. Guangdong, genit. prep. HHL- 2909 - 2; 14. A. sacculatus sp. n., male HT, China, Aut. Reg. Xizang, genit. prep. HHL- 2910 - 1; 15. A. sacculatus sp. n., male PT, China, Aut. Reg. Xizang, genit. prep. HHL- 2908 - 1." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/267006/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="215">Figs 14, 15</figureCitation>
