<figureCitation box="[299,329,1734,1758]" captionStart="FIGURES 30 – 32" captionStartId="7.[151,263,1840,1861]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1812]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,193,1818]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 30 – 32. Atrovirensis spp., male genitalia. 30. A. furcatus sp. n., HT, China, Prov. Guangdong, genit. prep. HHL- 2921 - 1; 31. A. sp. cf. furcatus, China, Prov. Guangdong, genit. prep. HHL- 2918 - 1; 32. A. sacculatus sp. n., HT, China, Aut. Reg. Xizang, genit. prep. HHL- 2910 - 1." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/267010/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="215">32</figureCitation>
